    <briefdescription>
<para>A <ref refid="d5/d05/classsgns_1_1crdt_1_1_d_a_g_syncer" kindref="compound">DAGSyncer</ref> is an abstraction to an IPLD-based p2p storage layer. A <ref refid="d5/d05/classsgns_1_1crdt_1_1_d_a_g_syncer" kindref="compound">DAGSyncer</ref> is a DAGService with the ability to publish new ipld nodes to the network, and retrieving others from it. </para>
